title: Economic Consequences Of A Vaccine Passport Mandate

opengraph.title: Economic Consequences Of A Vaccine Passport Mandate
opengraph.description: The amount of bureaucracy that would be added between the average consumer and everyday trade would be immense. Smaller businesses, which represent about half of the U.S. retail economy, would be under so much stress from maintaining the proper restrictions and adding infrastructure that they simply would not be able to compete with online retailers.
